article.description: — Houston Mallette’s 20 points helped Pepperdine defeat UC Irvine 64-55 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Mallette lifts Pepperdine to 64-55 victory over UC Irvine
article.linkText: Mallette lifts Pepperdine to 64-55 victory over UC Irvine
article.story: MALIBU, Calif. -- — Houston Mallette’s 20 points helped Pepperdine defeat UC Irvine 64-55 on Saturday night. Mallette added eight rebounds for the Waves (4-1). Maxwell Lewis scored nine points, while Boubacar Coulibaly finished with eight points, six rebounds and three blocks. Dawson Baker led the way for the Anteaters (3-1) with 12 points. UC Irvine also got nine points and 14 rebounds from Bent Leuchten. Devin Tillis had seven points and nine rebounds. NEXT UP Pepperdine next plays Wednesday against UCLA on the road, and UC Irvine will host Life Pacific on Monday. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
